#. Translators: Description that is shown if we couldn't load the video track
#. for the opened file (but possibly loaded audio).
#: src/video_preview.blp:20
msgid ""
"Maybe the file only has an audio track, or maybe the necessary video codec "
"is missing."
msgstr ""
"Ehtimol, faylda faqat audio trek mavjud yoki kerakli video kodek "
"oʻrnatilmagan boʻlishi mumkin."

