#. Translators: Description that is shown upon video preview loading error.
#: src/window.blp:155
msgid ""
"Please enter the start and end timestamps manually.\n"
"\n"
"If you're running Video Trimmer under Flatpak, note that opening files by drag-and-drop may not work."
